# FastlyGo Netlify Redirects

# www → non-www redirect (301 permanent)
https://www.fastlygo.mk/*  https://fastlygo.mk/:splat  301!
http://fastlygo.mk/*  https://fastlygo.mk/:splat  301!
http://www.fastlygo.mk/*  https://fastlygo.mk/:splat  301!

# Sitemap ve robots.txt - Manus backend'inden proxy (her zaman güncel)
/sitemap.xml  https://fastlygo.mk/sitemap.xml  200
/robots.txt   https://fastlygo.mk/robots.txt   200

# API isteklerini Manus backend'ine proxy'le
/api/*  https://fastlygo.mk/api/:splat  200

# SPA routing - tüm route'ları index.html'e yönlendir (en sona)
/*  /index.html  200
